###Block: Choose Bard Known Progression																																
Grant Highest Known only	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Bard Known Progression		DESC:This will manipulate your spells known to increase to the max highest allowed by the rules.	KEY:Bard Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Follow Standard Progression	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Bard Known Progression		DESC:This will follow the progression chart in the Player's Handbook.	KEY:Bard Known Progression ~ Follow Standard Progression																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Choose Own Progression	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Bard Known Progression		DESC:This will force the user to select spells each level.	KEY:Bard Known Progression ~ Choose Own Progression									BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Bard Known|4+(BardLVL>=2)+(BardLVL>=3)+(BardLVL>=4)+(BardLVL>=5)+(BardLVL>=6)+(BardLVL>=7)+(BardLVL>=8)+(BardLVL>=9)+if(BardLVL>=10,2,0)+(BardLVL>=11)+(BardLVL>=13)+if(BardLVL>=14,2,0)+(BardLVL>=15)+(BardLVL>=17)+if(BardLVL>=18,2,0)																		SOURCEPAGE:PHB
																																
