###Block: Choose Ranger Known Progression																																
Grant Highest Known only	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Ranger Known Progression		DESC:This will manipulate your spells known to increase to the max highest allowed by the rules.	KEY:Ranger Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only																											
