Choose Own Progression	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Ranger Known Progression		DESC:This will force the user to select spells each level.	KEY:Ranger Known Progression ~ Choose Own Progression									BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Ranger Known|if(RangerLVL>=2,2,0)+(RangerLVL>=3)+(RangerLVL>=5)+(RangerLVL>=7)+(RangerLVL>=9)+(RangerLVL>=11)+(RangerLVL>=13)+(RangerLVL>=15)+(RangerLVL>=17)																		
																																
