CATEGORY=Internal|Ranger Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|RangerKnown4|if(RangerLVL>=13,2,0)+(RangerLVL>=14)+if(RangerLVL>=15,2,0)+(RangerLVL>=16)-(RangerLVL>=20)																															
