###Block: Choose Sorcerer Known Progression
Grant Highest Known only	KEY:Sorcerer Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only			CATEGORY:Internal			TYPE:Sorcerer Known Progression	DESC:This will manipulate your spells known to increase to the max highest allowed by the rules.
Follow Standard Progression	KEY:Sorcerer Known Progression ~ Follow Standard Progression		CATEGORY:Internal			TYPE:Sorcerer Known Progression	DESC:This will follow the progression chart in the Player's Handbook.
Choose Own Progression		KEY:Sorcerer Known Progression ~ Choose Own Progression			CATEGORY:Internal			TYPE:Sorcerer Known Progression	DESC:This will force the user to select spells each level.	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Sorcerer Known|2+(SorcererLVL>=2)+(SorcererLVL>=3)+(SorcererLVL>=4)+(SorcererLVL>=5)+(SorcererLVL>=6)+(SorcererLVL>=7)+(SorcererLVL>=8)+(SorcererLVL>=9)+(SorcererLVL>=10)+(SorcererLVL>=11)+(SorcererLVL>=13)+(SorcererLVL>=15)+(SorcererLVL>=17)

# Grant Highest Known
CATEGORY=Internal|Sorcerer Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|SorcererKnown1|if(SorcererLVL>=1,2,0)+(SorcererLVL>=2)-(SorcererLVL>=3)-(SorcererLVL>=4)
CATEGORY=Internal|Sorcerer Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|SorcererKnown2|if(SorcererLVL>=3,2,0)+if(SorcererLVL>=4,2,0)-(SorcererLVL>=6)-(SorcererLVL>=7)-(SorcererLVL>=8)-(SorcererLVL>=9)
CATEGORY=Internal|Sorcerer Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|SorcererKnown3|if(SorcererLVL>=5,2,0)+if(SorcererLVL>=6,2,0)-(SorcererLVL>=10)-(SorcererLVL>=11)-(SorcererLVL>=12)-(SorcererLVL>=13)
CATEGORY=Internal|Sorcerer Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|SorcererKnown4|if(SorcererLVL>=7,2,0)+if(SorcererLVL>=8,2,0)-(SorcererLVL>=14)-(SorcererLVL>=15)-(SorcererLVL>=16)-(SorcererLVL>=17)
CATEGORY=Internal|Sorcerer Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|SorcererKnown5|if(SorcererLVL>=9,2,0)+(SorcererLVL>=12)
CATEGORY=Internal|Sorcerer Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|SorcererKnown6|if(SorcererLVL>=11,2,0)+(SorcererLVL>=12)
CATEGORY=Internal|Sorcerer Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|SorcererKnown7|if(SorcererLVL>=13,2,0)+(SorcererLVL>=14)
CATEGORY=Internal|Sorcerer Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|SorcererKnown8|if(SorcererLVL>=15,2,0)+(SorcererLVL>=16)
CATEGORY=Internal|Sorcerer Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|SorcererKnown9|if(SorcererLVL>=17,2,0)+(SorcererLVL>=18)+(SorcererLVL>=19)+(SorcererLVL>=20)

