###Block: Choose Wizard Known Progression
Grant Highest Known only	KEY:Wizard Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only			CATEGORY:Internal			TYPE:Wizard Known Progression	DESC:This will manipulate your spells known to increase to the max highest allowed by the rules.
Follow Standard Progression	KEY:Wizard Known Progression ~ Follow Standard Progression		CATEGORY:Internal			TYPE:Wizard Known Progression	DESC:This will follow the progression chart in the Player's Handbook.
Choose Own Progression		KEY:Wizard Known Progression ~ Choose Own Progression			CATEGORY:Internal			TYPE:Wizard Known Progression	DESC:This will force the user to select spells each level.	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Wizard Known|2+(WizardLVL>=2)+(WizardLVL>=3)+(WizardLVL>=4)+(WizardLVL>=5)+(WizardLVL>=6)+(WizardLVL>=7)+(WizardLVL>=8)+(WizardLVL>=9)+(WizardLVL>=10)+(WizardLVL>=11)+(WizardLVL>=13)+(WizardLVL>=15)+(WizardLVL>=17)

