CATEGORY=Internal|Wizard Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|WizardKnown2|if(WizardLVL>=3,2,0)+if(WizardLVL>=4,2,0)-(WizardLVL>=6)-(WizardLVL>=7)-(WizardLVL>=8)-(WizardLVL>=9)
CATEGORY=Internal|Wizard Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|WizardKnown3|if(WizardLVL>=5,2,0)+if(WizardLVL>=6,2,0)-(WizardLVL>=10)-(WizardLVL>=11)-(WizardLVL>=12)-(WizardLVL>=13)
