CATEGORY=Internal|Wizard Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|WizardKnown5|if(WizardLVL>=9,2,0)+(WizardLVL>=12)
CATEGORY=Internal|Wizard Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|WizardKnown6|if(WizardLVL>=11,2,0)+(WizardLVL>=12)
