CATEGORY=Internal|Wizard Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|WizardKnown8|if(WizardLVL>=15,2,0)+(WizardLVL>=16)
CATEGORY=Internal|Wizard Known Progression ~ Grant Highest Known only.MOD	BONUS:VAR|WizardKnown9|if(WizardLVL>=17,2,0)+(WizardLVL>=18)+(WizardLVL>=19)+(WizardLVL>=20)

